I saw Satan and a bunch of demons—these massive principalities—have a plan, and they were having a meeting and they were strategizing.

00:35:58.504 --> 00:36:05.638
You know, Satan can't be everywhere at once; he's only in one place at a time.

00:36:05.639 --> 00:36:16.159
And I saw him strategizing on how they can try to overthrow and derail the revival in the days ahead.

00:36:16.160 --> 00:36:24.239
God has a bigger plan; Satan has a little plan. And we know who's defeated—Satan is, by the blood of the Lamb.

00:36:24.240 --> 00:36:32.399
But he still tries. He still roars like a lion, but he doesn't have any teeth.

00:36:32.400 --> 00:36:36.233
He is a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour, the Bible says.

00:36:36.235 --> 00:36:40.518
But I believe he doesn't have any teeth when it comes to me. Why?

00:36:40.519 --> 00:36:46.632
Because we've got the blood and I apply the blood. This is just a representation, right?

00:36:46.633 --> 00:36:56.479
I anoint my house and my family. We take communion and we do this often in remembrance of Him.

00:36:56.480 --> 00:37:01.303
What did He do for you? That's the bottom line. What did Jesus Christ do for you?

00:37:01.304 --> 00:37:09.382
He made it where you can walk in victory over the devil. But the only way you will know it is by knowing the Word of God.

00:37:09.383 --> 00:37:15.249
You will know the truth and the truth will set you free. That's the only thing that's going to set you free.

00:37:15.250 --> 00:37:23.506
There is no Trump going to set you free. There's no FBI going to set you free. There's no super preacher that's going to set you free.

00:37:23.507 --> 00:37:35.039
The only thing that's ever going to set you free is knowing who you are in Christ. And for whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:37:35.040 --> 00:37:43.195
And when you know for whom the Son has set free is free indeed, that's you; that's me.

00:37:43.196 --> 00:37:49.598
I'm a believing believer that's not a doubter, and I'm an overcomer by the blood.

00:37:49.599 --> 00:37:53.604
And that's why we do this. We take it every day. Smith Wigglesworth did.

00:37:53.605 --> 00:38:06.526
I said, "Well, if Smith Wigglesworth did it and he raised the dead and did all that he did, well, I'm going to do it, too."How often is often?

00:38:06.527 --> 00:38:16.760
Every day in my house, sometimes twice. And reading the Bible—we leak out, so we keep...

00:38:16.761 --> 00:38:21.502
Smith Wigglesworth would read his Bible every 15 to 30 minutes.

00:38:21.503 --> 00:38:27.598
He would pull it out of his jacket pocket and he would remain full.

00:38:27.599 --> 00:38:35.417
Even if it was just a couple of scriptures, we must remain full for the days ahead.

00:38:35.418 --> 00:38:44.239
If you think you can believe God right now for a million dollars, you say, "Well, I'm believing for a million dollars,"but you don't have faith to believe for five.

00:38:44.240 --> 00:38:50.443
Start with one bite at a time. I'm believing God for five dollars.

00:38:50.444 --> 00:38:53.333
Believe for five dollars every day and watch it come to pass.

00:38:53.334 --> 00:39:04.879
Sow the seed. I'm believing God for a million already. Well, it's going from glory to glory to glory to glory.

00:39:04.880 --> 00:39:09.650
Don't bite off more than you can chew. Start with where your faith is at.

00:39:09.651 --> 00:39:15.838
Well, I'm at a million dollars. Have you believed for five dollars yet?

00:39:15.839 --> 00:39:22.719
We've got to be practical, and you sow your seed and you believe God for increase.

00:39:22.720 --> 00:39:27.798
Whatever you put your hands to will prosper. I believe in God-given miracles, ladies and gentlemen.

00:39:27.799 --> 00:39:32.097
I believe with all my heart, but I saw a lot of charismatic flakiness, too.

00:39:32.098 --> 00:39:40.078
And people always going out to the mailbox looking for their miracle, and they were always sitting on their blessed assurance doing nothing.

00:39:40.079 --> 00:39:49.439
Go out and put your boat into motion and do something with your hands, and God will bless whatever you put your hands to.

00:39:49.440 --> 00:39:53.514
But there's so many people with a welfare mentality thinking it's going to be given to them.

00:39:53.515 --> 00:39:58.101
And I believe that good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over will men give into our bosom.

00:39:58.102 --> 00:40:16.863
