We must pray for Trump, for the softness of his heart, and that he remains in Your hand, Lord.

02:14:01.280 --> 02:14:16.379
We pray for protection around our government officials. Thank you, Lord, for President Trump and his family.

02:14:16.380 --> 02:14:29.362
I believe they will stimulate the economy, and we will ride the wave. He will make great decisions to stimulate the economy.

02:14:29.363 --> 02:16:51.199
You don't realize how close the Tribulation is; it's rice paper thin.

02:16:51.200 --> 02:17:14.478
The end is rice paper thin. The storm that I see is so rice paper thin.

02:17:14.479 --> 02:17:56.478
If you truly realized how close the coming of the Lord is, it's not 'church as usual'anymore; it's 'church unusual.'From April 1st, the birthing pains are accelerating.

02:17:56.479 --> 02:18:33.358
Jesus is coming. In this next cycle, He has weighed you in the balance and found you lacking.

02:18:33.359 --> 02:19:01.358
I see the scales. A great shaking to awaken the bride and bring her to His side.

02:19:01.359 --> 02:19:25.119
Shaking to awaken. He said, 'Brandon, the remnant is awake.'I see so many who are sleeping.

02:19:25.120 --> 02:20:25.039
It's like a massive lake of molasses or tar where people are bobbing up and down. We cry for the harvest of those who are lost.

02:20:25.040 --> 02:20:52.300
There will be a day when you experience your last holidays—the last Christmas, the last Fourth of July, the last Memorial Day, Easter, and Thanksgiving.

02:20:52.301 --> 02:21:29.199
There will be a season when you say, 'That was the last one.'Jesus is coming.

02:21:29.200 --> 02:21:46.041
Brandon, there are moments like this where I don't want to leave because I can see the Tribulation and the next seven years so clearly.

02:21:46.042 --> 02:22:00.079
I see the peace agreement, Ezekiel 38 and 39, and the temple being built.

02:22:00.080 --> 02:22:34.879
It's so real I can touch it. I can see who the next president is.

02:22:34.880 --> 02:23:19.504
We must pray for Trump to make it full term, for his health, and for his decisions.

02:23:19.505 --> 02:23:30.251
Everything you know is about to change within a 24-hour period.

02:23:30.252 --> 02:23:35.839
Do you remember how September 11, 2001, changed everything so quickly?

02:23:35.840 --> 02:24:06.318
Air travel and homeland security changed; everything changed from that time forward.

02:24:06.319 --> 02:24:52.183
Everything is about to change again in a 24-hour period. It's an event that will be marked in history books; it changes the way you see life.

02:24:52.184 --> 02:25:44.875
Just as life changed after World War II and the Vietnam War, we have entered a point of no return since the UN meeting on September 23rd of last year.

02:25:44.876 --> 02:26:18.215
When we reach September 11th of this year, things will accelerate within that one-year window.

02:26:18.216 --> 02:26:40.639
Praise the Lord. I pray this blessed you tonight and that you feel refreshed.

02:26:40.640 --> 02:26:49.780
God bless you abundantly. Thank you for praying with me. Many hands make light work.

02:26:49.781 --> 02:27:36.079
We give all the glory to Jesus and tell of His wonderful love.

02:27:36.080 --> 02:27:44.033
Thank you for joining me. Remember, we love you. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

02:27:44.034 --> 02:27:52.070
Jesus loves you so much, and we love you. God bless you, and we'll see you again tomorrow night.

